{"pageProps":{"seo":{"title":"","description":"","keywords":"","image":"https://static.pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2019/05/main_home.jpg"},"content":{"title":"","description":""},"isWorkCase":true,"workCase":{"id":4048,"name":"Qtum Wallet","shortdescription":"Cryptocurrency Mobile Wallet for Android and iOS","description":"Multi-currency mobile crypto wallet with ERC20 token support, smart contract builder, and advanced security features.","preview":"https://pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/work-cryptocurrency-mobile-wallet-for-android-and-ios-1920.jpg","preview500":"https://pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/work-cryptocurrency-mobile-wallet-for-android-and-ios-544.jpg","preview768":"https://pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/work-cryptocurrency-mobile-wallet-for-android-and-ios-1024.jpg","alt":"The screenshot of UI of Qtum Wallet on a mobile phone","sections":[{"acf_fc_layout":"headdescription","button_text":"Share your idea","shortdescription":"Cryptocurrency Mobile Wallet for Android and iOS","description":"Multi-currency mobile crypto wallet with ERC20 token support, smart contract builder, and advanced security features","project_heading":"Project Goals","project_goal":"<p>Build a user-friendly mobile wallet for the Qtum blockchain platform enabling users to make transactions in multiple currencies while having all the capabilities of a modern crypto wallet such as Touch ID, 2FA protection, and transaction templates.</p>\n","technologyheading":"Work Done","technologiestags":[{"entry":"UI/UX design for Android and <a href=\"https://pixelplex.io/ios-app-development/\">iOS</a>"},{"entry":"Shamir’s secret encryption"},{"entry":"Secure Enclave and KeyStore support"},{"entry":"Qtum blockchain API integration"},{"entry":"Smart contracts template builder"}],"tags":[{"value":"Blockchain","label":"Blockchain"},{"value":"Mobile","label":"Mobile"},{"value":"Cryptocurrency","label":"Cryptocurrency"},{"value":"UI/UX","label":"UI/UX"},{"value":"Smart Contracts","label":"Smart Contracts"},{"value":"DApps","label":"DApps"}]},{"acf_fc_layout":"solutions","technologies":[{"title":"Swift","image":{"url":"https://pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/swift_icon.svg","alt":"Swift icon"}},{"title":"Kotlin","image":{"url":"https://pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/kotlin_icon.svg","alt":"Kotlin icon"}},{"title":"Node.js","image":{"url":"https://pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2019/07/node.svg","alt":"Node icon"}},{"title":"WebSocket","image":{"url":"https://pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/websocket_icon.svg","alt":"WebSocket icon"}},{"title":"MongoDB","image":{"url":"https://pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/07/mongodb_icon.svg","alt":"MongoDB icon"}},{"title":"Keychain","image":false},{"title":"DeepLink","image":false}],"rows":[{"title":"<h2>Solution</h2>\n","text":"<p>Our Qtum mobile cryptocurrency wallet is an easy-to-use yet powerful tool for multi-cryptocurrency management and tamper-proof peer-to-peer transactions, powered by client-side encryption and multifactor authentication.</p>\n"}]},{"acf_fc_layout":"twocolumnstext","description_top":"","slides":[{"image":{"url":"https://pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/qtum-wallet-slide-1-1600.jpg","alt":"Qtum Wallet dashboard and loginning screen"},"image_768":"https://pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/qtum-wallet-slide-1-768.jpg","image_500":"https://pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/qtum-wallet-slide-1-500.jpg","image_320":"https://pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/qtum-wallet-slide-1-320.jpg"},{"image":{"url":"https://pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/qtum-wallet-slide-2-1600.jpg","alt":"Qtum Wallet screens of transaction settings,and receipt"},"image_768":"https://pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/qtum-wallet-slide-2-768.jpg","image_500":"https://pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/qtum-wallet-slide-2-500.jpg","image_320":"https://pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/qtum-wallet-slide-2-320.jpg"},{"image":{"url":"https://pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/qtum-wallet-slide-3-1600.jpg","alt":"Qtum Wallet screens of settings, transaction, and code"},"image_768":"https://pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/qtum-wallet-slide-3-768.jpg","image_500":"https://pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/qtum-wallet-slide-3-500.jpg","image_320":"https://pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/09/qtum-wallet-slide-3-320.jpg"}],"rows":[{"title":"<h3>Top Security with Client-Side Encryption &amp; Muti-factor Authentication</h3>\n","text":"<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">With client-side encryption, the Qtum <a href=\"https://pixelplex.io/cryptocurrency-exchange-development/\">cryptocurrency mobile wallet</a> encodes private keys and all transaction data right on the mobile device. The user account, private keys, and all transactions are secured before any information reaches a third-party server.</span></p>\n<p>The wallet app is also backed with 2-factor authentication, PIN protection, an auto-lock feature, and Touch ID / Face ID biometric authentication.</p>\n"},{"title":"<h3>All the Essential Features Included</h3>\n","text":"<p>Qtum packs all the features needed in a mobile wallet to efficiently manage funds stored in multiple crypto-assets and easily make payments:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Integration with the top exchanges for buying and trading coins</li>\n<li>Multiple account management allowing customize, import, and export your settings</li>\n<li>Multiple currency support with ERC20 tokens</li>\n<li>Convenient interface displaying available coins, balances, and account history</li>\n<li>Private key back-up with a 12-word seed phrase</li>\n<li>Support for cold-storage account recovery</li>\n<li>QR Codes leading to a payment widget</li>\n<li>NFC support to streamline payments</li>\n<li>Transaction limits per day/week/month</li>\n<li>Notifications indicating completed transactions and exchange rate changes</li>\n</ul>\n"},{"title":"<h3>Smart Contract Builder and Transaction Templates</h3>\n","text":"<p>The mobile cryptocurrency wallet offers a user-friendly smart contract builder to help draft smart contracts and create transaction templates right from your mobile device. Just like with any other digital wallet, creating templates is a very convenient feature, especially when it saves you from inputting lengthy public keys.</p>\n"}],"title":"Details"},{"acf_fc_layout":"call_to_action","title":"Got an idea? Let’s work together","button_text":"Get in touch","background_rgb":"#64C7B4"},{"acf_fc_layout":"projectFeatures","title":"Project features","content":[{"title":"Multiple crypto asset support","image":{"url":"https://pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/multiple-cryptocurrency-support.svg","alt":"Blue icon of bitcoin coin"}},{"title":"Multi-factor authentication","image":{"url":"https://pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/use-of-smartphone-biometrics.svg","alt":"Blue icon of a fingerprint"}},{"title":"Shamir's Secret encryption","image":{"url":"https://pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/qtum-news-feed.svg","alt":"Blue icon of a document with horizontal lines"}},{"title":"QR code payment requests","image":{"url":"https://pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/qr-code-as-a-payment-request.svg","alt":"Blue icon of QR code processing"}},{"title":"iOS Secure Enclave & Android KeyStore support","image":{"url":"https://pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/multiple-platform-compatibility.svg","alt":"Blue icon of three connected tiling puzzle pieces"}},{"title":"Near Field Communication Support","image":{"url":"https://pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/real-time-transaction-history.svg","alt":"Blue icon of a document, clock, and quill pen"}},{"title":"Smart contract and transaction templates","image":{"url":"https://pixelplex.io/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/smart-contract-builder.svg","alt":"Blue icon of a document integrated into a net"}}]},{"acf_fc_layout":"relatedPosts","project":[774,1341]}],"seoTitle":"Qtum Wallet - Cryptoc